October 24 (Released) Jinan, Shandong. The following slogans were posted on the man's motorcycle:
In the future, the US dollar will be worthless. Immigrating to the United States now means joining the Kuomintang in 1948;
Taiwan's ending: peaceful reunification;
In the competition between China and the United States, China will win;
Some people always think that China cannot beat the United States. These people are used to being slaves.
